en-US.title: El Rio Health, Tucson
en-US.description: El Rio Health in Tucson, Arizona, is a community-focused health care center providing comprehensive, affordable and compassionate services. It dedicates specialized care to the transgender and gender non-conforming communities. The clinic offers a broad spectrum of services including behavioral health, dental care, and physical therapy, ensuring that all patients receive affirming, respectful, and quality healthcare regardless of their financial status.

address: 101 W Irvington Rd building 10, Tucson, AZ 85714, USA
